        "name": "Aldori Parry",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You can parry attacks against you with your Aldori dueling sword. Aldori dueling swords you're wielding gain the parry trait. If you have your other hand or hands free while wielding an Aldori dueling sword, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC while parrying instead of the usual +1.",
